---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import Cta from '../../components/Cta.astro';
import { articleSchema, breadcrumbSchema } from '../../lib/schema';
const path = '/archangels/';
const title = 'The Archangels: Names, Roles, Numbers & Colors';
const description = 'Meet the archangels — Michael, Gabriel, Raphael, Uriel and more — their roles, colors, and the numbers associated with each.';
const crumbs = [{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Archangels', href: path }];
const angels = [
  ['Michael', 'Protection, courage, cutting cords of fear.'],
  ['Gabriel', 'Messages, communication, creative announcement.'],
  ['Raphael', 'Healing of body and situation.'],
  ['Uriel', 'Wisdom, insight, the light in the intellect.'],
  ['Chamuel', 'Peace, finding what is lost, love repaired.'],
  ['Jophiel', 'Beauty, uplifted perception, gratitude.'],
  ['Zadkiel', 'Mercy, forgiveness, memory healed.'],
  ['Metatron', 'Sacred geometry of life, focus, ascension.'],
];
const schema = [articleSchema({ title, description, path }), breadcrumbSchema(crumbs)];
---
<Base title={title} description={description} schema={schema}>
  <div class="article">
    <Breadcrumbs crumbs={crumbs} />
    <header class="hero"><p class="eyebrow">Pillar Guide</p><h1>The Archangels</h1>
    <p class="lead">The names behind the numbers. This is the territory our brand is named for.</p></header>
    <p>Across traditions, archangels are the named intelligences associated with protection, healing, messages, and guidance — and each carries associated colors and numbers. Full individual profiles are being published; here is the map of who governs what.</p>
    <table><thead><tr><th>Archangel</th><th>Domain</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>{angels.map(([n, d]) => (<tr><td style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--gold-bright)">{n}</td><td>{d}</td></tr>))}</tbody></table>
    <p>Numbers and archangels interlock: repeating sequences are traditionally read as the signature of specific archangels. Start with the number that keeps finding you in the <a href="/angel-numbers/meanings/">meanings index</a>, or reveal the number you carry with the <a href="/angel-numbers/calculator/">calculator</a>.</p>
    <Cta />
  </div>
</Base>
